snippet.title: Wield the Techno-sword this March | Narita Boy Release Date Reveal
snippet.description:
Wield the Techno-sword and feel the Trichroma power within you in Narita Boy — releasing March 30th on PC, PS4, Nintendo Switch, and Xbox One!

Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1069530/Narita_Boy/

Play in a radical action-adventure as a legendary pixel hero, Narita Boy!! A computer is created by a genius programmer, a portal to the Digital Kingdom — a magical place beyond time and space. Discover the mysteries behind the Techno-sword and lock swords with the corrupt and tainted Stallions. A boy has been called, a hero will RISE — wield the Techno-sword and become a Legend! Save the world! 

Follow Studio Koba on Twitter: https://twitter.com/studiokobaGAME
Follow Team17 on Twitter: https://twitter.com/Team17
Like Team17 on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Team17/

About Team17 Digital Ltd
Founded in 1990, Team17 Digital Limited is a leading international games label that hosts the Worms franchise, Blasphemous, The Escapists, Moving Out, Overcooked, Neon Abyss, Going Under, Yooka-Laylee and many more from developers around the world. 

Visit www.team17.com for more info.
